data.description: Seller to contribute $10,000 towards buyer closing costs and prepaids with successful close of escrow on or before 12/31/2023.  Welcome to this stunning home built in 2020! This modern 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem boasts a spacious 3-car garage and is designed with an open-concept living space that's perfect for today's lifestyle. The kitchen takes center stage with a beautiful island that serves as a focal point. It's not just a place for culinary creations; it's a hub for connecting with family and friends. The front and back yards have been thoughtfully landscaped with low-maintenance desert plants to enjoy your outdoor spaces year-round. This home offers a perfect blend of contemporary design, functionality, and convenience. Whether you're looking for a cozy family retreat or a space to host gatherings, this 2020 home with its spacious layout and modern amenities is ready for you.
